column5: Mom sent me this pic yesterday.  Not sure where it came from I've never seen it before.     Dad got me started young.
Wow almost as tall as you!  still dreaming of my first fish half that size!  Nice fish!
Another case of the boy getting hooked better than the fish!!
wow, great way to get hooked on fishing....
beauty. and some day in the not too distant future, me thinks you will be taking a picture like that too
